trans-unit.source: Class JobHoldUntil is a printing attribute class, a date-time attribute, that specifies the exact date and time at which the job must become a candidate for printing.
trans-unit.target: 类JobHoldUntil是一个打印属性类,是一个日期-时间属性,它指定了作业必须成为打印候选的确切日期和时间。

trans-unit.source: Class JobImpressions is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the total size in number of impressions of the document(s) being submitted.
trans-unit.target: 类JobImpressions是一个整数值的打印属性类,指定了正在提交的文档的总印数大小。

trans-unit.source: Class JobImpressions is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the total size in number of impressions of the document(s) being submitted. An "impression" is the image (possibly many print-stream pages in different configurations) imposed onto a single media page.
trans-unit.target: JobImpressions 类是一个整数值的打印属性类,它指定了正在提交的文档的总尺寸(以印数为单位)。一个 "印迹 "是强加在单个介质页面上的图像(可能是不同配置的许多打印流页面)。

trans-unit.source: Class JobImpressionsCompleted is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the number of impressions completed for the job so far.
trans-unit.target: 类JobImpressionsCompleted是一个整数值的印刷属性类,它指定了到目前为止作业完成的印数。

trans-unit.source: Class JobImpressionsCompleted is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the number of impressions completed for the job so far. For printing devices, the impressions completed includes interpreting, marking, and stacking the output.
trans-unit.target: 类JobImpressionsCompleted是一个整数值的印刷属性类,它指定了到目前为止作业完成的印数。对于打印设备来说,完成的印数包括解释、标记和堆叠输出。

trans-unit.source: Class JobImpressionsSupported is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that gives the supported values for a JobImpressions attribute.
trans-unit.target: JobImpressionsSupported类是打印属性类，它是一组整数，为 JobImpressions 属性提供支持的值。

trans-unit.source: Class JobImpressionsSupported is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that gives the supported values for a JobImpressions attribute. It is restricted to a single contiguous range of integers; multiple non-overlapping ranges are not allowed. This gives the lower and upper bounds of the total sizes of print jobs in number of impressions that the printer will accept.
trans-unit.target: JobImpressionsSupported类是打印属性类，它是一组整数，为 JobImpressions 属性提供支持的值。它限于整数的单个连续范围；不允许多个非重叠范​​围。这给出了打印作业总大小的上限和下限，以打印机可接受的印数为单位。

trans-unit.source: Class JobKOctets is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the total size of the document(s) in K octets, i.e., in units of 1024 octets requested to be processed in the job.
trans-unit.target: JobKOctets 类是一个整数值的打印属性类,它以 K octets 为单位指定文档的总大小,即以 1024 octets 为单位,要求在作业中处理。

trans-unit.source: Class JobKOctets is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the total size of the document(s) in K octets, i.e., in units of 1024 octets requested to be processed in the job. The value must be rounded up, so that a job between 1 and 1024 octets must be indicated as being 1K octets, 1025 to 2048 must be 2K octets, etc. For a multidoc print job (a job with multiple documents), the JobKOctets value is computed by adding up the individual documents' sizes in octets, then rounding up to the next K octets value.
trans-unit.target: 类JobKOctets是一个整数值的打印属性类,它以K八位字节为单位指定文档的总大小,即以1024八位字节为单位要求在作业中处理。该值必须四舍五入,因此 1 至 1024 八位字节之间的作业必须表示为 1K 八位字节,1025 至 2048 为 2K 八位字节,等等。对于多文档打印作业(有多个文档的作业),JobKOctets值的计算方法是将各个文档的大小(以八位数为单位)相加,然后四舍五入到下一个K八位数。

trans-unit.source: Class JobKOctetsProcessed is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the total number of print data octets processed so far in K octets, i.e., in units of 1024 octets.
trans-unit.target: 类JobKOctetsProcessed是一个整数值的打印属性类,它以K八位数为单位,即以1024八位数为单位,指定到目前为止处理的打印数据八位数的总数。

trans-unit.source: Class JobKOctetsProcessed is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the total number of print data octets processed so far in K octets, i.e., in units of 1024 octets. The value must be rounded up, so that a job between 1 and 1024 octets inclusive must be indicated as being 1K octets, 1025 to 2048 inclusive must be 2K, etc. For a multidoc print job (a job with multiple documents), the JobKOctetsProcessed value is computed by adding up the individual documents' number of octets processed so far, then rounding up to the next K octets value.
trans-unit.target: JobKOctetsProcessed类是一个整数值的打印属性类,它指定了到目前为止处理的打印数据八位数的总数,单位是K八位数,即以1024八位数为单位。该值必须四舍五入,因此在1到1024八位字节(含)之间的作业必须表示为1K八位字节,1025到2048八位字节(含)必须表示为2K,等等。对于多文档打印作业(有多个文档的作业),JobKOctetsProcessed值的计算方法是将目前已处理的各个文档的八位数相加,然后四舍五入到下一个K八位数的值。

trans-unit.source: Class JobKOctetsSupported is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that gives the supported values for a JobKOctets attribute.
trans-unit.target: JobKOctetsSupported类是打印属性类，它是一组整数，为 JobKOctets 属性提供支持的值。

trans-unit.source: Class JobKOctetsSupported is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that gives the supported values for a JobKOctets attribute. It is restricted to a single contiguous range of integers; multiple non-overlapping ranges are not allowed. This gives the lower and upper bounds of the total sizes of print jobs in units of K octets (1024 octets) that the printer will accept.
trans-unit.target: JobKOctetsSupported类是打印属性类，它是一组整数，为 JobKOctets 属性提供支持的值。它限于整数的单个连续范围；不允许多个非重叠范​​围。这样就给出了打印机可接受的K个八位字节（1024个八位字节）单位的打印作业总大小的上限和下限。

trans-unit.source: Class JobMediaSheets is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the total number of media sheets to be produced for this job.
trans-unit.target: 类JobMediaSheets是一个整数值的印刷属性类,它指定了该作业要生产的介质页总数。

trans-unit.source: Class JobMediaSheetsCompleted is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the number of media sheets which have completed marking and stacking for the entire job so far, whether those sheets have been processed on one side or on both.
trans-unit.target: 类JobMediaSheetsCompleted是一个整数值的印刷属性类,它指定了到目前为止整个作业中已经完成标记和堆叠的介质张数,无论这些介质张数是在一面还是两面都进行了处理。

trans-unit.source: Class JobMediaSheetsSupported is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that gives the supported values for a JobMediaSheets attribute.
trans-unit.target: JobMediaSheetsSupported类是打印属性类，它是一组整数，为 JobMediaSheets 属性提供受支持的值。

trans-unit.source: Class JobMediaSheetsSupported is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that gives the supported values for a JobMediaSheets attribute. It is restricted to a single contiguous range of integers; multiple non-overlapping ranges are not allowed. This gives the lower and upper bounds of the total sizes of print jobs in number of media sheets that the printer will accept.
trans-unit.target: JobMediaSheetsSupported类是打印属性类，它是一组整数，为 JobMediaSheets 属性提供受支持的值。它限于整数的单个连续范围；不允许多个非重叠范​​围。这给出了打印机可以接受的介质张数中打印作业总大小的上限和下限。

trans-unit.source: Class JobMessageFromOperator is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that provides a message from an operator, system administrator, or "intelligent" process to indicate to the end user the reasons for modification or other management action taken on a job.
trans-unit.target: 类JobMessageFromOperator是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,它提供了来自操作员、系统管理员或 "智能 "进程的信息,以向最终用户表明对作业进行修改或其他管理操作的原因。

trans-unit.source: Class JobName is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that specifies the name of a print job.
trans-unit.target: 类JobName是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,用于指定打印作业的名称。

trans-unit.source: Class JobName is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that specifies the name of a print job. A job's name is an arbitrary string defined by the client. It does not need to be unique between different jobs. A Print Job's JobName attribute is set to the value supplied by the client in the Print Request's attribute set. If, however, the client does not supply a JobName attribute in the Print Request, the printer, when it creates the Print Job, must generate a JobName. The printer should generate the value of the Print Job's JobName attribute from the first of the following sources that produces a value: (1) the DocumentName attribute of the first (or only) doc in the job, (2) the URL of the first (or only) doc in the job, if the doc's print data representation object is a URL, or (3) any other piece of Print Job specific and/or document content information.
trans-unit.target: JobName类是打印属性类，它是一个文本属性，用于指定打印作业的名称。作业的名称是客户端定义的任意字符串。在不同的作业之间不必是唯一的。将打印作业的JobName属性设置为客户端在“打印请求”属性集中提供的值。但是，如果客户端未在“打印请求”中提供JobName属性，则打印机在创建“打印作业”时必须生成一个JobName。打印机应从以下产生值的第一个来源中生成“打印作业”的JobName属性的值：（1） DocumentName 作业中第一个（或唯一）文档的属性，（2）如果该文档的打印数据表示对象是URL，则该作业中第一个（或唯一）文档的URL，或（3）任何其他Print作业特定和/或文档内容信息。

trans-unit.source: Class JobOriginatingUserName is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that contains the name of the end user that submitted the print job.
trans-unit.target: 类JobOriginatingUserName是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,包含提交打印作业的最终用户的名称。

trans-unit.source: Class JobOriginatingUserName is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that contains the name of the end user that submitted the print job. If possible, the printer sets this attribute to the most authenticated printable user name that it can obtain from the authentication service that authenticated the submitted Print Request. If such is not available, the printer uses the value of the RequestingUserName attribute supplied by the client in the Print Request's attribute set. If no authentication service is available, and the client did not supply a RequestingUserName attribute, the printer sets the JobOriginatingUserName attribute to an empty (zero-length) string.
trans-unit.target: JobOriginatingUserName类是打印属性类，是一个文本属性，其中包含提交打印作业的最终用户的名称。如果可能，打印机将此属性设置为可从对提交的打印请求进行身份验证的身份验证服务获得的最可验证的可打印用户名。如果不可用，则打印机将使用客户端在“打印请求”的属性集中提供的 RequestingUserName 属性的值。如果没有可用的身份验证服务，并且客户端未提供 RequestingUserName 属性，则打印机会将JobOriginatingUserName属性设置为空（零长度）字符串。

trans-unit.source: Class JobPriority is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies a print job's priority.
trans-unit.target: 类JobPriority是一个整数值的打印属性类,用于指定打印作业的优先级。

trans-unit.source: Class JobPrioritySupported is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies whether a Print Service instance supports the JobPriority attribute and the number of different job priority levels supported.
trans-unit.target: JobPrioritySupported类是一个整数值的打印属性类，它指定打印服务实例是否支持 JobPriority 属性以及支持的不同作业优先级的数量。

trans-unit.source: Class JobSheets is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that determines which job start and end sheets, if any, must be printed with a job.
trans-unit.target: 类JobSheets是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,它决定一个作业必须打印哪些作业开始和结束页(如果有的话)。

trans-unit.source: Class JobSheets is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that determines which job start and end sheets, if any, must be printed with a job. Class JobSheets declares keywords for standard job sheets values. Implementation- or site-defined names for a job sheets attribute may also be created by defining a subclass of class JobSheets.
trans-unit.target: 类JobSheets是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,它决定了哪些作业开始和结束页(如果有的话)必须与作业一起打印。类JobSheets声明了标准作业页值的关键字。也可以通过定义类JobSheets的子类来创建作业单属性的实现或站点定义的名称。

trans-unit.source: Class JobStateReason is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that provides additional information about the job's current state, i.e., information that augments the value of the job's JobState attribute.
trans-unit.target: JobStateReason类是打印属性类，它是一个枚举，它提供有关作业当前状态的附加信息，即，增加作业 JobState 属性值的信息。

trans-unit.source: Class JobStateReason is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that provides additional information about the job's current state, i.e., information that augments the value of the job's JobState attribute. Class JobStateReason defines standard job state reason values. A Print Service implementation only needs to report those job state reasons which are appropriate for the particular implementation; it does not have to report every defined job state reason.
trans-unit.target: JobStateReason类是打印属性类，它是一个枚举，它提供有关作业当前状态的其他信息，即，增加作业 JobState 属性值的信息。 JobStateReason类定义标准的作业状态原因值。打印服务实施仅需要报告适合于特定实施的那些工作状态原因；它不必报告每个定义的作业状态原因。

trans-unit.source: Class JobStateReasons inherits its implementation from class java.util.HashSet. Unlike most printing attributes which are immutable once constructed, class JobStateReasons is designed to be mutable; you can add JobStateReason objects to an existing JobStateReasons object and remove them again. However, like class java.util.HashSet, class JobStateReasons is not multiple thread safe. If a JobStateReasons object will be used by multiple threads, be sure to synchronize its operations (e.g., using a synchronized set view obtained from class java.util.Collections).
trans-unit.target: JobStateReasons类从 java.util.HashSet 类继承其实现。与大多数打印属性一旦构造就不可变的不同，JobStateReasons类被设计为可变的。您可以将 JobStateReason 对象添加到现有JobStateReasons对象，然后再次将其删除。但是，与类 java.util.HashSet 一样，JobStateReasons类也不是多线程安全的。如果JobStateReasons对象将由多个线程使用，请确保同步其操作（例如，使用从类 java.util.Collections 获得的同步设置视图）。

trans-unit.source: Class JobStateReasons is a printing attribute class, a set of enumeration values, that provides additional information about the job's current state, i.e., information that augments the value of the job's JobState attribute.
trans-unit.target: JobStateReasons类是打印属性类，它是一组枚举值，它提供有关作业当前状态的附加信息，即，增加作业 JobState 属性值的信息。
类 键盘聚焦管理器

trans-unit.source: Class Media is a printing attribute class that specifies the medium on which to print.
trans-unit.target: 类介质是一个打印属性类,指定打印的介质。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaName currently declares a few standard media names. Implementation- or site-defined names for a media name attribute may also be created by defining a subclass of class MediaName.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaName目前声明了一些标准的媒体名称。也可以通过定义类MediaName的子类来创建媒体名称属性的实现或站点定义的名称。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaName is a subclass of Media, a printing attribute class (an enumeration) that specifies the media for a print job as a name.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaName是Media的一个子类,是一个打印属性类(枚举),将打印作业的介质指定为名称。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaPrintableArea is a printing attribute used to distinguish the printable and non-printable areas of media.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaPrintableArea是一个打印属性,用于区分介质的可打印和不可打印区域。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSize is a two-dimensional size valued printing attribute class that indicates the dimensions of the medium in a portrait orientation, with the X dimension running along the bottom edge and the Y dimension running along the left edge.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaSize是一个二维尺寸值的印刷属性类,它表示介质在纵向的尺寸,X尺寸沿底边,Y尺寸沿左边。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSize is a two-dimensional size valued printing attribute class that indicates the dimensions of the medium in a portrait orientation, with the X dimension running along the bottom edge and the Y dimension running along the left edge. Thus, the Y dimension must be greater than or equal to the X dimension. Class MediaSize declares many standard media size values, organized into nested classes for ISO, JIS, North American, engineering, and other media.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaSize是一个二维尺寸值的印刷属性类,它表示介质在纵向的尺寸,X尺寸沿底边,Y尺寸沿左边。因此,Y维必须大于或等于X维。类MediaSize声明了许多标准的介质尺寸值,组织成嵌套类,用于ISO、JIS、北美、工程和其他介质。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSize.Engineering includes MediaSize values for engineering media.
trans-unit.target: MediaSize.Engineering类包含工程媒体的 MediaSize 值。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSize.ISO includes MediaSize values for ISO media.
Class MediaSize.JIS includes MediaSize values for JIS (Japanese) media.
trans-unit.target: MediaSize.JIS类包含JIS（日语）媒体的 MediaSize 值。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSize.JIS includes MediaSize values for JIS (Japanese) media. *
trans-unit.target: MediaSize.JIS类包含JIS（日语）媒体的 MediaSize 值。*

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSize.NA includes MediaSize values for North American media.
trans-unit.target: MediaSize.NA类包含北美媒体的 MediaSize 值。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSize.Other includes MediaSize values for miscellaneous media.
trans-unit.target: MediaSize.Other类包含其他媒体的 MediaSize 值。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSizeName currently declares a few standard media name values.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaSizeName目前声明了几个标准的媒体名称值。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaSizeName is a subclass of Media.
Class MediaTray declares keywords for standard media kind values. Implementation- or site-defined names for a media kind attribute may also be created by defining a subclass of class MediaTray.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaTray声明了标准媒体种类值的关键字。也可以通过定义类MediaTray的子类来创建媒体种类属性的实现或站点定义的名称。

trans-unit.source: Class MediaTray is a subclass of Media.

Class MediaTray is a subclass of Media. Class MediaTray is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that specifies the media tray or bin for the job. This attribute can be used instead of specifying MediaSize or MediaName.
trans-unit.target: 类MediaTray是Media的一个子类。Class MediaTray 是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,用于指定作业的介质盘或仓。这个属性可以用来代替指定MediaSize或MediaName。

trans-unit.source: Class MultipleDocumentHandling is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that controls finishing operations and the placement of one or more print-stream pages into impressions and onto media sheets.
trans-unit.target: 类MultipleDocumentHandling是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,用于控制精加工操作以及将一个或多个打印流页面放置到印模和介质页上。

trans-unit.source: Class MultipleDocumentHandling is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that controls finishing operations and the placement of one or more print-stream pages into impressions and onto media sheets. When the value of the Copies attribute exceeds 1, MultipleDocumentHandling also controls the order in which the copies that result from processing the documents are produced. This attribute is relevant only for a multidoc print job consisting of two or more individual docs.
trans-unit.target: 类MultipleDocumentHandling是一个打印属性类，它是一个枚举，它控制修整操作以及将一个或多个打印流页面放置在印张和介质纸上的位置。当“ Copies 属性的值超过1时，MultipleDocumentHandling还将控制处理文档所产生的副本的顺序。此属性仅与包含两个或多个单独文档的多文档打印作业相关。
类导航过滤器.过滤器旁路

trans-unit.source: Class NumberOfDocuments is an integer valued printing attribute that indicates the number of individual docs the printer has accepted for this job, regardless of whether the docs' print data has reached the printer or not.
trans-unit.target: 类NumberOfDocuments是一个整数值的打印属性,表示打印机已经接受了这项作业的单个文档的数量,无论文档的打印数据是否已经到达打印机。

trans-unit.source: Class NumberOfInterveningJobs is an integer valued printing attribute that indicates the number of jobs that are ahead of this job in the relative chronological order of expected time to complete (i.e., the current scheduled order).
trans-unit.target: 类NumberOfInterveningJobs是一个整数值的打印属性,它表示按预计完成时间的相对时间顺序(即当前的计划顺序)排在这个作业前面的作业数量。

trans-unit.source: Class NumberUp is an integer valued printing attribute class that specifies the number of print-stream pages to impose upon a single side of an instance of a selected medium.
trans-unit.target: 类NumberUp是一个整数值的打印属性类,它指定了对所选介质实例的单面施加的打印流页数。

trans-unit.source: Class NumberUpSupported is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that gives the supported values for a NumberUp attribute.
trans-unit.target: NumberUpSupported类是打印属性类，它是一组整数，为 NumberUp 属性提供受支持的值。

trans-unit.source: Class OrientationRequested is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that indicates the desired orientation for printed print-stream pages; it does not describe the orientation of the client-supplied print-stream pages.
trans-unit.target: 类OrientationRequested是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,用于指示打印流页面所需的方向,它并不描述客户端提供的打印流页面的方向。

trans-unit.source: Class OutputDeviceAssigned is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that identifies the output device to which the service has assigned this job.
trans-unit.target: 类OutputDeviceAssigned是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,用于标识服务将此作业分配给的输出设备。

trans-unit.source: Class OutputDeviceAssigned is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that identifies the output device to which the service has assigned this job. If an output device implements an embedded Print Service instance, the printer need not set this attribute. If a print server implements a Print Service instance, the value may be empty (zero- length string) or not returned until the service assigns an output device to the job. This attribute is particularly useful when a single service supports multiple devices (so called "fan-out").
trans-unit.target: 类 OutputDeviceAssigned 是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,用于标识服务将此作业分配给的输出设备。如果输出设备实现了嵌入式打印服务实例,则打印机无需设置此属性。如果打印服务器实现了打印服务实例,则该值可能为空(零长度字符串),或者在服务为作业分配输出设备之前不返回。当一个服务支持多个设备(即所谓的 "扇出")时,该属性特别有用。

trans-unit.source: Class PDLOverrideSupported is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that expresses the printer's ability to attempt to override processing instructions embedded in documents' print data with processing instructions specified as attributes outside the print data.
trans-unit.target: 类PDLOverrideSupported是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,表达了打印机试图用打印数据之外的属性指定的处理指令覆盖文档打印数据中嵌入的处理指令的能力。

trans-unit.source: Class PageRanges is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that identifies the range(s) of print-stream pages that the Printer object uses for each copy of each document which are to be printed.
trans-unit.target: PageRanges 类是一个打印属性类,是一组整数,用于标识打印机对象用于打印每个文档副本的打印流页面范围。

trans-unit.source: Class PageRanges is a printing attribute class, a set of integers, that identifies the range(s) of print-stream pages that the Printer object uses for each copy of each document which are to be printed. Nothing is printed for any pages identified that do not exist in the document(s). The attribute is associated with
trans-unit.target: PageRanges 类是一个打印属性类,是一组整数,用于标识打印机对象用于打印每个文档的每个副本的打印流页面范围。对于文档中不存在的任何页面,将不会打印。该属性与

trans-unit.source: Class PagesPerMinute is an integer valued printing attribute that indicates the nominal number of pages per minute to the nearest whole number which may be generated by this printer (e.g., simplex, black-and-white).
trans-unit.target: 类PagesPerMinute是一个整数值的打印属性,它表示每分钟的标称页数,以最接近的整数表示,这可能是由该打印机产生的(例如,单面、黑白)。

trans-unit.source: Class PagesPerMinute is an integer valued printing attribute that indicates the nominal number of pages per minute to the nearest whole number which may be generated by this printer (e.g., simplex, black-and-white). This attribute is informative, not a service guarantee. Generally, it is the value used in the marketing literature to describe the device. A value of 0 indicates a device that takes more than two minutes to process a page.
trans-unit.target: 类 PagesPerMinute 是一个整数值的打印属性,表示每分钟的标称页数,以最接近的整数表示,可由该打印机生成(例如,单面、黑白)。该属性是信息性的,不是服务保证。一般来说,它是营销文献中用来描述设备的值。值为0表示设备处理一页纸的时间超过两分钟。

trans-unit.source: Class PagesPerMinuteColor is an integer valued printing attribute that indicates the nominal number of pages per minute to the nearest whole number which may be generated by this printer when printing color (e.g., simplex, color).
trans-unit.target: 类PagesPerMinuteColor是一个整数值的打印属性,表示每分钟的标称页数,到最接近的整数,当打印彩色(例如,单面、彩色)时,该打印机可能会产生。

trans-unit.source: Class PagesPerMinuteColor is an integer valued printing attribute that indicates the nominal number of pages per minute to the nearest whole number which may be generated by this printer when printing color (e.g., simplex, color). For purposes of this attribute, "color" means the same as for the ColorSupported attribute, namely, the device is capable of any type of color printing at all, including highlight color as well as full process color. This attribute is informative, not a service guarantee. Generally, it is the value used in the marketing literature to describe the color capabilities of this device. A value of 0 indicates a device that takes more than two minutes to process a page. If a color device has several color modes, it may use the pages-per- minute value for this attribute that corresponds to the mode that produces the highest number.
trans-unit.target: PagesPerMinuteColor类是一个整数值的打印属性，它指示每分钟的标称页数到最接近的整数，该整数可能由该打印机在打印颜色（例如，单面，彩色）时生成。就此属性而言，“颜色”的含义与 ColorSupported 的含义相同。属性，即该设备完全能够进行任何类型的彩色打印，包括突出显示颜色以及全彩色。此属性是提供信息的，不是服务保证。通常，它是市场营销文献中用来描述此设备色彩功能的价值。值0表示设备花费超过两分钟的时间来处理页面。如果彩色设备具有多种颜色模式，则它可以使用此属性的每分钟页面数，该值与产生最大数字的模式相对应。

trans-unit.source: Class PresentationDirection is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that is used in conjunction with the NumberUp attribute to indicate the layout of multiple print-stream pages to impose upon a single side of an instance of a selected medium.
trans-unit.target: PresentationDirection类是一个打印属性类，它是一个枚举，与 NumberUp 属性结合使用，以指示要施加到所选介质实例的单面的多个打印流页面的布局。

trans-unit.source: Class PresentationDirection is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that is used in conjunction with the NumberUp attribute to indicate the layout of multiple print-stream pages to impose upon a single side of an instance of a selected medium. This is useful to mirror the text layout conventions of different scripts. For example, English is "toright-tobottom", Hebrew is "toleft-tobottom" and Japanese is usually "tobottom-toleft".
trans-unit.target: PresentationDirection类是一个打印属性类，它是一个枚举，与 NumberUp 属性结合使用，以指示要施加到所选介质实例的单面的多个打印流页面的布局。这对于镜像不同脚本的文本布局约定很有用。例如，英语是“从右到下”，希伯来语是“从左到下”，日语通常是“从左到右”。

trans-unit.source: Class PrintEvent is the super class of all Print Service API events.
trans-unit.target: 类PrintEvent是所有打印服务API事件的超级类。

trans-unit.source: Class PrintException encapsulates a printing-related error condition that occurred while using a Print Service instance.
trans-unit.target: PrintException类封装了使用打印服务实例时发生的与打印相关的错误条件。

trans-unit.source: Class PrintException encapsulates a printing-related error condition that occurred while using a Print Service instance. This base class furnishes only a string description of the error. Subclasses furnish more detailed information if applicable.
trans-unit.target: PrintException 类封装了使用打印服务实例时发生的与打印相关的错误条件。该基类仅提供错误的字符串描述。如果适用,子类将提供更详细的信息。

trans-unit.source: Class PrintJobAttributeEvent encapsulates an event a PrintService reports to let the client know that one or more printing attributes for a PrintJob have changed.
trans-unit.target: PrintJobAttributeEvent类封装了一个PrintService报告的事件,让客户端知道PrintJob的一个或多个打印属性发生了变化。

trans-unit.source: Class PrintQuality is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that specifies the print quality that the printer uses for the job.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrintQuality 是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,用于指定打印机对作业使用的打印质量。

trans-unit.source: Class PrintServiceAttributeEvent encapsulates an event a Print Service instance reports to let the client know of changes in the print service state.
trans-unit.target: PrintServiceAttributeEvent类封装了打印服务实例报告的事件,以让客户端了解打印服务状态的变化。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterInfo is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that provides descriptive information about a printer.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrinterInfo 是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,它提供了关于打印机的描述性信息。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterInfo is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that provides descriptive information about a printer. This could include things like: "This printer can be used for printing color transparencies for HR presentations", or "Out of courtesy for others, please print only small (1-5 page) jobs at this printer", or even \ "This printer is going away on July 1, 1997, please find a new printer".
trans-unit.target: PrinterInfo类是打印属性类，它是一种文本属性，它提供有关打印机的描述性信息。这可能包括了诸如： "This printer can be used for printing color transparencies for HR presentations" ，或 "Out of courtesy for others, please print only small (1-5 page) jobs at this printer" ，甚至是\ "This printer is going away on July 1, 1997, please find a new printer" 。
类 打印机正在接受工作

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterIsAcceptingJobs is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that indicates whether the printer is currently able to accept jobs.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrinterIsAcceptingJobs是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,表示打印机当前是否能够接受作业。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterIsAcceptingJobs is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that indicates whether the printer is currently able to accept jobs. This value is independent of the PrinterState and PrinterStateReasons attributes because its value does not affect the current job; rather it affects future jobs. If the value is NOT_ACCEPTING_JOBS, the printer will reject jobs even when the PrinterState is IDLE. If value is ACCEPTING_JOBS, the Printer will accept jobs even when the PrinterState is STOPPED.
trans-unit.target: PrinterIsAcceptingJobs类是打印属性类，它是一个枚举，它指示打印机当前是否能够接受作业。此值独立于 PrinterState 和 PrinterStateReasons 属性，因为它的值不影响当前作业；而是影响未来的工作。如果值为NOT_ACCEPTING_JOBS，则即使 PrinterState 为IDLE ，打印机也会拒绝作业。如果值为ACCEPTING_JOBS，则即使 PrinterState 为STOPPED ，打印机也将接受作业。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterLocation is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that identifies the location of the device.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterLocation是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,用于标识设备的位置。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterLocation is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that identifies the location of the device. This could include things like: "in Room 123A, second floor of building XYZ".
trans-unit.target: PrinterLocation类是打印属性类，它是一种文本属性，用于标识设备的位置。其中可能包括： "in Room 123A, second floor of building XYZ" 。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterMakeAndModel is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that the make and model of the printer.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrinterMakeAndModel 是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,即打印机的品牌和型号。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterMessageFromOperator is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that provides a message from an operator, system administrator, or "intelligent" process to indicate to the end user information about or status of the printer, such as why it is unavailable or when it is expected to be available.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrinterMessageFromOperator 是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,它提供了来自操作员、系统管理员或 "智能 "进程的消息,以向最终用户指示有关打印机的信息或状态,例如为什么它不可用或预计何时可用。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterMoreInfo is a printing attribute class, a URI, that is used to obtain more information about this specific printer.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterMoreInfo是一个打印属性类,是一个URI,用于获取该特定打印机的更多信息。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterMoreInfo is a printing attribute class, a URI, that is used to obtain more information about this specific printer. For example, this could be an HTTP type URI referencing an HTML page accessible to a web browser. The information obtained from this URI is intended for end user consumption. Features outside the scope of the Print Service API can be accessed from this URI. The information is intended to be specific to this printer instance and site specific services (e.g. job pricing, services offered, end user assistance).
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterMoreInfo是一个打印属性类,是一个URI,用于获取该特定打印机的更多信息。例如,这可以是一个HTTP类型的URI,引用一个可被Web浏览器访问的HTML页面。从该URI获取的信息仅供最终用户使用。打印服务API范围以外的功能可以通过该URI访问。该信息旨在针对该打印机实例和站点的特定服务(例如作业定价、提供的服务、终端用户协助)。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterMoreInfoManufacturer is a printing attribute class, a URI, that is used to obtain more information about this type of device.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterMoreInfoManufacturer是一个打印属性类,是一个URI,用于获取该类型设备的更多信息。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterMoreInfoManufacturer is a printing attribute class, a URI, that is used to obtain more information about this type of device. The information obtained from this URI is intended for end user consumption. Features outside the scope of the Print Service API can be accessed from this URI (e.g., latest firmware, upgrades, service proxies, optional features available, details on color support). The information is intended to be germane to this kind of printer without regard to site specific modifications or services.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterMoreInfoManufacturer是一个打印属性类,是一个URI,用于获取该类型设备的更多信息。从这个URI获得的信息是为了供最终用户消费。打印服务API范围之外的功能可以从该URI访问(例如,最新的固件、升级、服务代理、可用的可选功能、颜色支持的详细信息)。这些信息旨在适用于此类打印机,而不考虑特定站点的修改或服务。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterName is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that specifies the name of a printer.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterName是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,用于指定打印机的名称。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterName is a printing attribute class, a text attribute, that specifies the name of a printer. It is a name that is more end-user friendly than a URI. An administrator determines a printer's name and sets this attribute to that name. This name may be the last part of the printer's URI or it may be unrelated. In non-US-English locales, a name may contain characters that are not allowed in a URI.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrinterName 是一个打印属性类,是一个文本属性,用于指定打印机的名称。它是一个比URI更方便最终用户使用的名称。管理员确定打印机的名称并将此属性设置为该名称。该名称可能是打印机URI的最后一部分,也可能与打印机无关。在非美英地区,名称可能包含URI中不允许使用的字符。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterResolution is a printing attribute class that specifies an exact resolution supported by a printer or to be used for a print job.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrinterResolution 是一个打印属性类,它指定了打印机支持的确切分辨率或用于打印作业的分辨率。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterResolution is a printing attribute class that specifies an exact resolution supported by a printer or to be used for a print job. This attribute assumes that printers have a small set of device resolutions at which they can operate rather than a continuum.
trans-unit.target: 类 PrinterResolution 是一个打印属性类,它指定了打印机支持的确切分辨率或用于打印作业的分辨率。该属性假定打印机有一小部分设备分辨率,它们可以在这些分辨率下工作,而不是连续的。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterState is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that identifies the current state of a printer.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterState是一个打印属性类,是一个枚举,用于标识打印机的当前状态。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterState is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that identifies the current state of a printer. Class PrinterState defines standard printer state values. A Print Service implementation only needs to report those printer states which are appropriate for the particular implementation; it does not have to report every defined printer state. The PrinterStateReasons attribute augments the PrinterState attribute to give more detailed information about the printer in given printer state.
trans-unit.target: PrinterState类是打印属性类，它是一个枚举，用于标识打印机的当前状态。PrinterState类定义标准的打印机状态值。打印服务实施仅需要报告适用于特定实施的那些打印机状态；它不必报告每个定义的打印机状态。该 PrinterStateReasons 属性扩充了PrinterState属性，以提供有关在给定的打印机状态下打印机的更多详细信息。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterStateReason is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that provides additional information about the printer's current state, i.e., information that augments the value of the printer's PrinterState attribute.
trans-unit.target: PrinterStateReason类是打印属性类，它是一个枚举，它提供有关打印机当前状态的附加信息，即，增加打印机的 PrinterState 属性值的信息。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterStateReason is a printing attribute class, an enumeration, that provides additional information about the printer's current state, i.e., information that augments the value of the printer's PrinterState attribute. Class PrinterStateReason defines standard printer state reason values. A Print Service implementation only needs to report those printer state reasons which are appropriate for the particular implementation; it does not have to report every defined printer state reason.
trans-unit.target: PrinterStateReason类是打印属性类，它是一个枚举，它提供有关打印机当前状态的附加信息，即，增加打印机的 PrinterState 属性值的信息。PrinterStateReason类定义标准的打印机状态原因值。打印服务实施仅需要报告适用于特定实施的那些打印机状态原因；它不必报告每个定义的打印机状态原因。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterStateReasons inherits its implementation from class java.util.HashMap. Each entry in the map consists of a PrinterStateReason object (key) mapping to a Severity object (value):
trans-unit.target: PrinterStateReasons类从 java.util.HashMap 类继承其实现。映射中的每个条目都包含一个映射到 Severity 对象（值）的 PrinterStateReason 对象（键）：

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterStateReasons is a printing attribute class, a set of enumeration values, that provides additional information about the printer's current state, i.e., information that augments the value of the printer's PrinterState attribute.
trans-unit.target: PrinterStateReasons类是打印属性类，它是一组枚举值，它提供有关打印机当前状态的其他信息，即，增加打印机的 PrinterState 属性值的信息。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterURI is a printing attribute class, a URI, that specifies the globally unique name of a printer.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterURI是一个打印属性类,是一个URI,指定打印机的全局唯一名称。

trans-unit.source: Class PrinterURI is a printing attribute class, a URI, that specifies the globally unique name of a printer. If it has such a name, an administrator determines a printer's URI and sets this attribute to that name.
trans-unit.target: 类PrinterURI是一个打印属性类,是一个URI,指定打印机的全局唯一名称。如果它有这样的名称,管理员就会确定打印机的URI,并将此属性设置为该名称。

trans-unit.source: Class QueuedJobCount is an integer valued printing attribute that indicates the number of jobs in the printer whose JobState is either PENDING, PENDING_HELD, PROCESSING, or PROCESSING_STOPPED.
trans-unit.target: QueuedJobCount类是一个整数值的打印属性，它指示 JobState 为PENDING，PENDING_HELD，PROCESSING或PROCESSING_STOPPED 的打印机中的作业数。
